text:
Keeping an eye on the exciting Romanian elections.

@Mircea_Geoana, my friend of over 20 years, is in a close-heated race for the presidency. He is the former @NATO Deputy Secretary General and former Romanian ambassador to the United States. He led the founding of the Romania caucus in the U.S. House of Representatives, which I co-chair. He’s pro-NATO and pro-U.S.

As we face Putin’s continued aggression, strength among our allies is essential. Mircea Geoana worked with the first Trump Administration and is well known. He has been a great partner. This is a race to watch.
